qas.question: Which newspaper has a significantly higher circulation, The Sunday Times or The Times?
As of January 2013, The Times has a circulation of how many people?
As of January 2013, The Sunday Times has a circulation of how many people?

context: <a0_0>The Sunday Times<a0_0/> has a significantly higher circulation than The Times, and sometimes outsells The Sunday Telegraph. As of January 2013, The Times has a circulation of <a1_0>399,339<a1_0/> and The Sunday Times of <a2_0>885,612<a2_0/>.
